Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,————————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教皇圣下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣下被…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退 全员撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,————————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.95,0:00:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.26,0:00:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人 不行 振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:02.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'LL BE THERE FOR YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:02.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'LL BE THERE FOR YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:05.22,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽ばたいて行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:05.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飞出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:11.64,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新しい世界へ GO WITH ME
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:11.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着崭新的世界 GO WITH ME
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:20.17,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手と手を繋いで進めば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:20.17,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要手牵手一起前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:22.92,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇さえ恐れず行けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:22.92,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连黑暗也无足为惧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:27.86,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰もまだ知らないあの場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:27.86,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着未曾有人知晓的那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:31.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,途中で嵐に遭っても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:31.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算途中遭遇暴风雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:34.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見守る瞳の灯りが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:34.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你守望的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:38.45,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立ち向かう勇気をくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:38.45,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给予了我奋勇抗争的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.93,0:01:44.46,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法より強い力さ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.93,0:01:44.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是比魔法更强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:50.45,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かけがえのない君を思う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:50.45,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要心怀无可替代的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:55.78,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この場 ALL RIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:55.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立于此地 ALL RIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.11,0:01:58.96,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから I'LL BE THERE FOR YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.11,0:01:58.96,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 I'LL BE THERE FOR YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:01.60,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絆を信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:01.60,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信你我之间的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.61,0:02:07.37,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂しさも唇も強気な眼差しも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.61,0:02:07.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的寂寞 你的嘴唇 你的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:10.18,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好きさ ALWAYS I LOVE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:10.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都喜欢哦  ALWAYS I LOVE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:12.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らなら出来る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:12.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的话一定可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:18.49,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷ついて 乗り越えて 心から笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:18.49,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路受伤一路克服 发自真心的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:25.19,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新しい世界へ GO WITH ME
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:25.19,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着崭新的世界 GO WITH ME
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了 搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德鲁弗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德鲁弗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律特斯的贝尔萨尔提宫殿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律特斯的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:03:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 远古巨龙呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.81,0:03:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨龙怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止活动了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就在快要穿过奥鲁奇亚溪谷的时候 突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个大块头就像岩石一样蜷成一团不动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是因为教皇圣下的力量导致巨龙死亡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 非常遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是能持续听到巨龙的脉搏声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与心跳相呼应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久后就会醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不仅于此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.11,0:03:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥斯曼院长 您也来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教皇圣下的事真的很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 现在的当务之急是要把远古巨龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣下也一定是如此期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 叫老夫前来应该就是为了那远古巨龙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 奥斯曼院长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您一边担任魔法学园的院长 一边进行研究的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那家伙还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下次我们一定要打败它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给教皇报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 露易丝 蒂法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪丝塔 有什么吃的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我马上去把汤热一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 学院的大家呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像都回托里斯汀了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露可夏娜小姐他们说是要一起去才人先生的宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以倒是留下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 但是估计还要过一段时间才能回宅邸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去帮雪丝塔的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不…下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人没说一句有关德鲁弗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实他明明非常悲伤的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…因为才人先生他很坚强啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定在竭尽全力的忍耐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不坚强也没有关系！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他索性就说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“没有德鲁弗就不能战斗了”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“不会再使用里维斯拉谢尔的力量了”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在责怪蒂法你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:05:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再看到才人继续削减自己的生命了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望才人死去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于远古巨龙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老夫翻阅文献得到的结论就是以上这些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 对于露易丝和蒂法妮娅来说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待她们的是前所未有的残酷试炼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.51,0:06:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 关于这件事 之后老夫打算亲自告诉她们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在“四之四”没有齐聚的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样对抗巨龙是不是个错误啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 根据传说所言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去打倒巨龙的是“四之四”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 并没有说除了他们之外 其他人就什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 在这六千年里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的文明也急速发展
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的哈尔凯尼亚 还存在着超越国界的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:07:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也许就能填补尚且欠缺的“四之四”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特女王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托里斯汀会全军出动对抗此次灾厄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知高卢可否与我们一起并肩作战？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.51,0:07:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也去请求罗马尼亚和其他各国的协助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈尔凯尼亚的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我们自己的双手来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了对抗巨龙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以组建了哈尔凯尼亚全土的联军？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 由我来指挥全军
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 远古巨龙不靠我们这些“虚无继承者”的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝 我们所有人都是出生于哈尔凯尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由哈尔凯尼亚养育长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以面对这种世界危机我们无法袖手旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算机会渺茫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也会为打倒巨龙的可能性而放手一搏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也打算一起奔赴战场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 只要还有一口气在就会继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为出生于哈尔凯尼亚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向这个世界献出我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起克服这次危机吧 绝对可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为出生于哈尔凯尼亚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向这个世界献出我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是哈尔凯尼亚人 所以这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是才人他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人并不是在这个世界出生的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他牵扯进来真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快做好出征的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去打倒巨龙了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别落队了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须得干啊 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可不是伤感的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧？德鲁弗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？沉没在我绿洲里的机器？是指那个铁筒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算利用那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那东西已经坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在妖精的国度里 有没有别的那种东西啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被慎重的保管在某处之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 没听说过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为搞不好有可能呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有战斗机的话 远古巨龙什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就能打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西是叫做战斗机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是我那个世界的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以在空中高速飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 用导弹的话连军舰都能击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这么厉害的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先回一趟你的国家 再把它拿过来不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个的话稍微有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很远吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么使用露易丝的魔法如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指世界之门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事能办得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有办不到的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…我的世界啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意试试？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试着用世界之门连接才人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果顺利的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人 我们一起去拿那个战斗机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 干吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 确认一下步骤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先露易丝向才人的国家打开一扇窗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs30}再利用才人的力量把窗户扩大到可以让人通过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是他在指挥啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs30}然后才人跟露易丝两人一起前往才人的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他喜欢这样啦 就睁一只眼闭一只眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到战斗机后再次利用露易丝的魔法回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能回到我的世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加油喔 才人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那差不多该开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人 伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我稍微借用一下才人的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你那个世界的印象传送给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs42}（咒语）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 通往才人世界的大门啊 打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的建筑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是才人先生的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝 是我的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝 过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 才人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能与你相遇 真的很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请你记得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后我展现给你的表情…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是笑容喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝 你做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露…露易丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦利埃尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干了什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了打败巨龙 他是不可或缺的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人他…是从别的世界过来的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要让他承担这个世界的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕他是虚无的使魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦利埃尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人 才人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝小姐是真心爱着才人先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话 是不会做出这种选择的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝 露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人先生他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我把他送回原本的世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万分抱歉 但是…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一定会做同样的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔帕莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 肯定这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不借助里维斯拉谢尔的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会靠我自身的力量打倒巨龙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会赌上自己的一切 加入战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去魔法学院啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实好像过去封印了远古巨龙的是虚无的继承者们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从文献来看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎继承者们也同时给予了远古巨龙力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透过被巨龙吞食
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨龙透过吞食虚无而变得强大起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.79,0:15:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此那家伙会凭藉本能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着虚无继承者的所在地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:16:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 巨龙一开始前往罗马利亚是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为感受到了虚无继承人之一的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教皇圣下他的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 等到那家伙醒来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来盯上的人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我或者是蒂法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才把你们带回魔法学院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的话 周围没有什么集落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无需担心民众被牵扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,针对已经预料到的巨龙行进路线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队也准备好了尽可能的利用炮击拖住巨龙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道能起多大的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过应该能争取一些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要是在魔法学院战斗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学院里的人该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯尔贝尔老师已经指挥大家去避难了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪丝塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了要你和露可夏娜他们去宅邸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已经来了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我拜托她的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我很想见识一下魔法学院嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这里很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也都去避难了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 露易丝 蒂法妮娅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家正在商量我想出的 为了打败巨龙的阵型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 你们两个快过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔帕莎小姐 你刚才不是还在王宫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用最快速度飞过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就赶超过你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.98,0:17:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 奥斯曼院长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不听我的话 都留下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我早就料到会这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在这里的话也许会死的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么可能置身事外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也想保护自己生活的这个世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们“水精灵骑士队”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:18:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有代替才人保护你们的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这种事 不觉得有些刺激吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰奈特 为什么你们会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我雇用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是佣兵 认钱不认人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为同伴来说 我们还是蛮可靠的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我们 也不希望世界毁灭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能多一个先住魔法的使用者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能省去很多功夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 露可夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 不过如果能在这里阻止巨龙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是为了涅夫提斯好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 要吃夜宵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我在那个时候露出了那种窝囊的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让我继续使用里维斯拉谢尔的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝才会做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 如果没有这个力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是无法打倒远古巨龙的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…露易丝会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定那里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 这里打开了一扇光之门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就被召唤过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得到吗 露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝 露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是被喜欢的女仆给甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.29,0:20:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 难不成你在哭鼻子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这熊样肯定要被甩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了闭上你们的狗嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我们费了这么多劲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果这家伙身上一分钱都没有 白费劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠我一个人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是无法回到哈尔凯尼亚的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…再也见不到面了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在成长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等巨大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:20:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙快退下 退下！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正前方有什么东西正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说从正面而来？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远古巨龙！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没听说那家伙还能飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上进行攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:07.30,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,めちゃめちゃ大好き
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:07.30,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级无敌喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.31,0:22:10.09,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でもでもムカつく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.31,0:22:10.09,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是好生气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:12.80,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キスしてお願い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:12.80,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了给我一个吻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.82,0:22:16.05,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キスシテ↑アゲナイ↓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.82,0:22:16.05,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不给你甜吻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:19.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,はらはら イライラその態度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:19.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人担心不已 焦躁不已的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:22.37,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別にヤキモチじゃないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:22.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不是在吃醋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:25.70,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほらほら チラチラ誰見てるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:25.70,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂我说 你到底在偷看谁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:27.65,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ありえないでしょう それって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:27.65,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事完全不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:30.90,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ゼロからあなたをしつけなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:30.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得从零开始好好调教你才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:32.76,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍛え直してあげるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:32.76,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你脱胎换骨的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.79,0:22:37.10,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひざまずいたら ワンと鳴きなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.79,0:22:37.10,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快给我跪下 然后大叫一声汪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.11,0:22:38.72,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早くお坐り！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.11,0:22:38.72,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点给我坐下！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:44.90,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙女心は微妙(だけと敏感だ)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:44.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女心思如此微妙（却也敏感）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.92,0:22:50.02,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当は胸がいっぱいなの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.92,0:22:50.02,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你早就已经填满了我的胸口喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:50.52,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あんた鈍感！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:50.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是太迟钝了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.91,0:22:53.81,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全密着 そばにいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.91,0:22:53.81,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲密无间 待在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:56.11,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断然 私を愛して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:56.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毅然坚决 要爱着我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.14,0:22:59.18,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋する女の子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.14,0:22:59.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为恋爱中的女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:02.15,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やっぱり欲張りなんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:02.15,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然都是贪心鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:04.70,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間接着 抱き寄せて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:04.70,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬间靠近 紧紧抱着我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.72,0:23:07.30,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,単純 つまりは夢中に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.72,0:23:07.30,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单纯无比 也就是迷恋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.31,0:23:10.08,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飽きれるくらいにね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.31,0:23:10.08,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用多到让我觉得厌烦的爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.09,0:23:14.91,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私だけに恋をして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.09,0:23:14.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅爱着我直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:15.61,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,めちゃめちゃ大好き
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:15.61,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级无敌喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.45,0:23:18.34,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でもでもムカつく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.45,0:23:18.34,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是好生气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:21.01,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キスしてお願い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:21.01,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了给我一个吻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.01,0:23:24.56,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キスシテ↑アゲナイ↓けど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.01,0:23:24.56,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我才不给你甜吻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.87,0:23:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经不在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.27,0:23:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你一定在属于你的世界里生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一点都不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.92,0:23:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 最终话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零之使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.71,0:23:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人 一直以来谢谢你了
